&lt;h3 class=&quot;col-md-6 pull-left&quot;&gt;YOUR CHALLENGE:&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;col-md-6 pull-left&quot;&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;border&quot;&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p8i6j01 paragraph&quot;&gt;As an FP&amp;amp;A Manager at Blacklane, you will enable better decision-making through clear financial reporting, high-quality analysis, and strong business partnership across the organization. You will work closely with Finance leadership and cross-functional stakeholders to turn data into insight, support planning and performance management, and help drive business results.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p8i6j01 paragraph&quot;&gt;You will:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul class=&quot;p8i6j07 p8i6j02&quot;&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;p8i6j0a&quot;&gt;Deliver financial analysis that supports leadership decision-making, performance reviews, and business planning&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;p8i6j0a&quot;&gt;Partner closely with stakeholders across Finance and the business to understand performance drivers, risks, and opportunities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;p8i6j0a&quot;&gt;Support month-end, forecast, budget, and long-range planning processes with high-quality analysis and insights&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;p8i6j0a&quot;&gt;Translate financial and operational data into actionable recommendations for business teams and leadership&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;p8i6j0a&quot;&gt;Help improve planning, reporting, and analytical processes to increase efficiency, consistency, and scalability&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;p8i6j0a&quot;&gt;Contribute to ad hoc projects, business cases, and strategic analyses as Blacklane continues to grow&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;br&gt;
