&lt;p class=&quot;p8i6j01 paragraph&quot;&gt;You have:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul class=&quot;p8i6j07 p8i6j02&quot;&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;p8i6j0a&quot;&gt;2–3 years of experience in FP&amp;amp;A, corporate finance, or a related analytical finance role&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;p8i6j0a&quot;&gt;Experience with both internal and external reporting&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;p8i6j0a&quot;&gt;Strong skills in financial analysis, budgeting, forecasting, and performance tracking&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;p8i6j0a&quot;&gt;Proven ability to act as a business partner and work effectively with non-finance stakeholders&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;p8i6j0a&quot;&gt;Experience working with large datasets and turning them into clear insights and recommendations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;p8i6j0a&quot;&gt;Strong Excel / Google Sheets skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;p8i6j0a&quot;&gt;Experience with BI or planning tools, such as Workday Adaptive Planning, is a plus&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;p8i6j0a&quot;&gt;You bring solid experience in financial consolidations across multiple entities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;p8i6j0a&quot;&gt;Excellent communication skills in English, with the ability to explain financial topics clearly to different audiences&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p8i6j01 paragraph&quot;&gt;Bonus points if you have:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul class=&quot;p8i6j07 p8i6j02&quot;&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;p8i6j0a&quot;&gt;Experience in a scaling, international environment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;p8i6j0a&quot;&gt;Exposure to board, investor, or management reporting processes&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
