&lt;h3&gt;The Mission: Platform as a Product&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Your mission is to bridge the gap between &quot;infrastructure&quot; and &quot;developer success&quot;. You will transform our platform from a set of tools and processes into a cohesive internal product. You will lead a team of engineers through a period of growth and establish a &quot;paved road&quot; that allows our product teams to ship with zero friction.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;The Impact: Driving High-Velocity Delivery&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You aren&#39;t inheriting a fixed roadmap or team, you are shaping it! Working together with our Staff Engineer, you will define what good looks like and how to become a high performing team. You will oversee delivery timelines, scope and are not afraid of making highly impactful decisions. You don’t care about the ticket throughput, you care about work done.&lt;/p&gt;
